  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nIf type or paste scrollable text message into the input field of any chat and try to place the cursor to some specific place in the text, it will jump to another random place.\r\nCursor placement works fine with long press.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nCan set the cursor to any place in long text with a quick tap.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/110649856-4a934e00-81ba-11eb-85ac-e0647c859941.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open chat\r\n- Paste a long message into the input field\r\n- Scroll the message a little\r\n- Tap on some place in the text to set the cursor\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: Nightly\r\n- Operating System: iOS\r\n",
